<h1>Privacy Policy for Lavenavuna</h1>
<p><strong>Effective Date: 2025</strong></p>

<p>Lavenavuna (“we”, “us”, “our”) is a digital creator brand focused on winter fashion, minimalist home décor, and lifestyle content. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect information when users interact with our website, services, social media channels, Pinterest content, and affiliate programs.</p>

<h2>Information We Collect</h2>
<p>We may collect:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Non-personal device information</li>
  <li>IP addresses</li>
  <li>Browsing interactions</li>
  <li>Affiliate tracking data</li>
</ul>

<h2>How We Use Information</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Improve user experience</li>
  <li>Enhance our content and recommendations</li>
  <li>Analyze traffic patterns</li>
  <li>Support affiliate tracking (Amazon, Pinterest, ShopStyle, Spring Store)</li>
</ul>

<h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
<p>We work with:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Amazon Associates</li>
  <li>Pinterest</li>
  <li>Linktree</li>
  <li>Google Services</li>
  <li>Spring/Teespring Store</li>
</ul>

<h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
<p>Lavenavuna participates in affiliate programs. We may earn commissions when you click or purchase through links in our content.</p>

<h2>Data Protection</h2>
<p>We follow industry-standard practices to safeguard non-personal information.</p>

